ComicInfo.Title: My Roommate's Stuff
ComicInfo.Summary:
Rest Your Gun Here: A couple engages in sex on a shooting range.
KX2: Two roommates get Valentine's Day presents for each other.
Quick Shot: An unsatisfied female tries to solve her problem with firearms.
How Much Can You Handle?: A very small male tries to sexually satisfy a very large female.
Outta Date: A litany of The Artist's failed attempts at attracting women.
My Roommate's Stuff: A woman, playing with her ex-roommate's sex toys, becomes an aggressive sub the moment she puts on a leather collar.
